headline: What Analysts Think of Costco Stock Ahead of Earnings
summary: Costco Wholesale is set to report its results for the third quarter of fiscal 2025 after the bell on Thursday, with analysts bullish on the retailer's stock, but not expecting substantial share- price gains.

headline: Walmart, Costco, and even Dollar General are getting into the gas station business
summary: Major retailers like Costco (COST), Sam’s Club, and Walmart (WMT) are stepping on the gas even as the age of electric vehicles creeps closer. These big box stores — traditionally not a place for pumps, unless they are the kind sold in the shoe aisle — are turning into gas giants, expanding their hours, adding car capacity, and building more infrastructure
